### Example
```
# Single Genome Mode
CampyCPS -f /PATH_TO_ASSEBLED_GENOME/sample.fa -o PATH_TO_OUTPUT

# Batch Mode
CampyCPS -i /PATH_TO_ASSEBLED_GENOME_DIR -o PATH_TO_OUTPUT
```


